ms-center gap-8\"><a class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-electric-blue border border-electric-blue/30 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:bg-electric-blue hover:text-white transition-all animate-pulse\" href=\"/immersive\">Immersive Universe</a><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"#services\">Services<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"/training\">Training<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"/resources\">Resources<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"/portfolio\">Company<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><a class=\"bg-electric-blue text-white px-6 py-2 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-electric-blue-lt transition-colors rounded-sm\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></nav><main class=\"flex-grow\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 py-20 max-w-4xl\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6\">Untitled</h1><p class=\"text-gold mb-10\"></p><div class=\"prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none\"><p class=\"mb-4\">---\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">title: &quot;Local SEO for Nigerian Businesses: Dominate Google Maps &amp; Business Profiles&quot;\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">date: &quot;2025-01-15T00:00:00Z&quot;\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">description: &quot;Complete local SEO guide. Optimize your Google Business Profile, citations, and location pages to rank in Nigerian Google Maps.&quot;\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">---\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">Hephzibah Media\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      - [Services](index.html#services)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      - [About](about.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      - [Landing Pages](landing-pages-sales-funnels.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      - [Training](training.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      - [Get a Quote](contact.html&quot; class=&quot;nav-cta)\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      Local SEO · 10 min read\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">      # Local SEO for Nigerian Businesses: Dominate Google Maps &amp; Business Profiles\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      By Hephzibah Media Team · Published December 22, 2024\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">      Local SEO wins the &#x27;near me&#x27; searches. When someone searches &#x27;web design Lagos&#x27; or &#x27;printing services Abuja,&#x27; Google shows map results + local businesses. Here&#x27;s exactly how to rank at the top of those results.\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## Claim &amp; Optimize Your Google Business Profile\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">1. Go to google.com/business, search your business name. 2. If it exists, claim it. If not, create it. 3. Complete 100% of the profile: all photos, description, hours, services, website. 4. Add 1015 photos (office, team, past work, before-afters). 5. Verify via postcard (23 weeks) or phone (instant). Verified profiles rank 23× higher.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## NAP Consistency Across the Web\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">NAP = Name, Address, Phone. Every mention of your business must be identical: same spelling, same format. Create citations on: Google Business, Bing Places, Nigerian directories (VConnect, BusinessList.com.ng, Jumia Services). Update all of them if you move. Inconsistent NAP = lower local rankings.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## Location Pages with Unique Content\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">If you serve multiple cities (Lagos, Abuja, Ikeja), create a unique page for each. Not just swapping the city name  genuinely different content: local testimonials, local case studies, community involvement. Example: &#x27;Web Design in Lagos&#x27; page mentions Lekki-specific clients; &#x27;Web Design in Abuja&#x27; page mentions GRA Abuja clients.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## Build Local Backlinks\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">Get mentioned on Nigerian media sites, blogs, and business networks. Write a guest post for a Lagos business blog. Sponsor a local event (gets mentioned on their website). Partner with complementary businesses who link to you. Local links signal &#x27;this business serves this community.&#x27;\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## Reviews: The Local SEO Multiplier\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">Google prioritises businesses with recent 5-star reviews. Aim for 40+ reviews (threshold for competitive rankings). After every project, email customers: &#x27;We&#x27;d love your feedback on Google [link].&#x27; Respond to every review (positive and negative). Reviews also influence CTR  4.5? businesses get 25% more clicks than 3.5?.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## Question &amp; Answer Management\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">Go to your Google Business Profile, add FAQs. Customers see these before they call or visit. Example: &#x27;How much does web design cost?&#x27; &#x27;Do you offer payment plans?&#x27; Answer in 23 sentences, clearly. This also helps Google understand your business better.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## Local Schema Markup\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">Add LocalBusiness schema to your website (already done in these templates). Include: address, phone, hours, service areas. If you serve 10 cities, add ServiceArea schema listing all of them. This helps Google understand your service radius.\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">    ## Ready for Growth?\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">Let our team audit your current marketing strategy and show you exactly what&#x27;s holding you back.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">    [Start Your Free Audit](contact.html&quot; class=&quot;btn-primary)\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">        Hephzibah Media\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">Nigeria&#x27;s premium Digital Marketing, Tech &amp; Print Agency. Building brands that dominate from Ogere, Ogun State.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">        Old Ode Road, Along Ogere Tollgate, Ogere, Nigeria\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">        Services\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Web Design](web-design.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Digital Marketing](digital-marketing.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [SEO](seo.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Graphics Design](graphics-design.html)\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">        Resources\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Blog](blog.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Portfolio](portfolio.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [About Us](about.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Contact](contact.html)\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">        Connect\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [WhatsApp](https://wa.me/2349077780156)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Email](mailto:hello@hephzibahmedia.com.ng)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Instagram](https://instagram.com/hephzibahmedia&quot; rel=&quot;noopener)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [LinkedIn](https://linkedin.com/company/hephzibahmedia&quot; rel=&quot;noopener)\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      © 2026 Hephzibah Media. All rights reserved.\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">      Built for speed. Engineered to rank.\r</p><br/></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-midnight-mid border-t border-white/10 pt-20 pb-10\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 group\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"relative w-8 h-8 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Hephzibah Media Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"1