\\"p\\\",\\\"34\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"      ## Claim \\u0026 Optimize Your Google Business Profile\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"35\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"36\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"37\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"1. Go to google.com/business, search your business name. 2. If it exists, claim it. If not, create it. 3. Complete 100% of the profile: all photos, description, hours, services, website. 4. Add 1015 photos (office, team, past work, before-afters). 5. Verify via postcard (23 weeks) or phone (instant). Verified profiles rank 23× higher.\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"38\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"39\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"      ## NAP Consistency Across the Web\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"40\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"41\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"42\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"NAP = Name, Address, Phone. Every mention of your business must be identical: same spelling, same format. Create citations on: Google Business, Bing Places, Nigerian directories (VConnect, BusinessList.com.ng, Jumia Services). Update all of them if you move. Inconsistent NAP = lower local rankings.\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"43\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"44\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"      ## Location Pages with Unique Content\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"45\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"46\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"47\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"If you serve multiple cities (Lagos, Abuja, Ikeja), create a unique page for each. Not just swapping the city name  genuinely different content: local testimonials, local case studies, community involvement. Example: 'Web Design in Lagos' page mentions Lekki-specific clients; 'Web Design in Abuja' page mentions GRA Abuja clients.\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"48\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"49\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"      ## Build Local Backlinks\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"50\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"51\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"52\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Get mentioned on Nigerian media sites, blogs, and business networks. Write a guest post for a Lagos business blog. Sponsor a local event (gets mentioned on their website). Partner with complementary businesses who link to you. Local links signal 'this business serves this community.'\\\\r\\\"}],\\\"$L1e\\\",\\\"$L1f\\\",\\\"$L20\\\",\\\"$L21\\\",\\\"$L22\\\",\\\"$L23\\\",\\\"$L24\\\",\\\"$L25\\\",\\\"$L26\\\",\\\"$L27\\\",\\\"$L28\\\",\\\"$L29\\\",\\\"$L2a\\\",\\\"$L2b\\\",\\\"$L2c\\\",\\\"$L2d\\\",\\\"$L2e\\\",\\\"$L2f\\\",\\\"$L30\\\",\\\"$L31\\\",\\\"$L32\\\",\\\"$L33\\\",\\\"$L34\\\",\\\"$L35\\\",\\\"$L36\\\",\\\"$L37\\\",\\\"$L38\\\",\\\"$L39\\\",\\\"$L3a\\\",\\\"$L3b\\\",\\\"$L3c\\\",\\\"$L3d\\\",\\\"$L3e\\\",\\\"$L3f\\\",\\\"$L40\\\",\\\"$L41\\\",\\\"$L42\\\",\\\"$L43\\\",\\\"$L44\\\",\\\"$L45\\\",\\\"$L46\\\",\\\"$L47\\\",\\\"$L48\\\",\\\"$L49\\\",\\\"$L4a\\\",\\\"$L4b\\\",\\\"$L4c\\\",\\\"$L4d\\\",\\\"$L4e\\\",\\\"$L4f\\\",\\\"$L50\\\",\\\"$L51\\\",\\\"$L52\\\",\\\"$L53\\\",\\\"$L54\\\",\\\"$L55\\\",\\\"$L56\\\",\\\"$L57\\\",\\\"$L58\\\",\\\"$L59\\\",\\\"$L5a\\\",\\\"$L5b\\\",\\\"$L5c\\\",\\\"$L5d\\\",\\\"$L5e\\\",\\\"$L5f\\\",\\\"$L60\\\",\\\"$L61\\\",\\\"$L62\\\",\\\"$L63\\\",\\\"$L64\\\",\\\"$L65\\\",\\\"$L66\\\",\\\"$L67\\\",\\\"$L68\\\",\\\"$L69\\\",\\\"$L6a\\\",\\\"$L6b\\\",\\\"$L6c\\\",\\\"$L6d\\\",\\\"$L6e\\\"]}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1e:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"53\\\",{}]\\n1f:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"54\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"      ## Reviews: The Local SEO Multiplier\\\\r\\\"}]\\n20:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"55\\\",{}]\\n21:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"56\\\",{}]\\n22:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\