",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"19\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"20\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"21\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"22\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"23\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"24\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      Local SEO · 10 min read\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"25\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      # Local SEO for Nigerian Businesses: Dominate Google Maps & Business Profiles\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"26\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"27\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      By Hephzibah Media Team · Published December 22, 2024\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"28\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      Local SEO wins the 'near me' searches. When someone searches 'web design Lagos' or 'printing services Abuja,' Google shows map results + local businesses. Here's exactly how to rank at the top of those results.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"29\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"30\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"31\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"32\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"33\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"34\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Claim & Optimize Your Google Business Profile\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"35\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"36\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"37\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"1. Go to google.com/business, search your business name. 2. If it exists, claim it. If not, create it. 3. Complete 100% of the profile: all photos, description, hours, services, website. 4. Add 1015 photos (office, team, past work, before-afters). 5. Verify via postcard (23 weeks) or phone (instant). Verified profiles rank 23× higher.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"38\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"39\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## NAP Consistency Across the Web\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"40\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"41\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"42\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"NAP = Name, Address, Phone. Every mention of your business must be identical: same spelling, same format. Create citations on: Google Business, Bing Places, Nigerian directories (VConnect, BusinessList.com.ng, Jumia Services). Update all of them if you move. Inconsistent NAP = lower local rankings.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"43\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"44\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Location Pages with Unique Content\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"45\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"46\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"47\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"If you serve multiple cities (Lagos, Abuja, Ikeja), create a unique page for each. Not just swapping the city name  genuinely different content: local testimonials, local case studies, community involvement. Example: 'Web Design in Lagos' page mentions Lekki-specific clients; 'Web Design in Abuja' page mentions GRA Abuja clients.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"48\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"49\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Build Local Backlinks\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"50\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"51\",{}],\"$L2\",\"$L3\",\"$L4\",\"$L5\",\"$L6\",\"$L7\",\"$L8\",\"$L9\",\"$La\",\"$Lb\",\"$Lc\",\"$Ld\",\"$Le\",\"$Lf\",\"$L10\",\"$L11\",\"$L12\",\"$L13\",\"$L14\",\"$L15\",\"$L16\",\"$L17\",\"$L18\",\"$L19\",\"$L1a\",\"$L1b\",\"$L1c\",\"$L1d\",\"$L1e\",\"$L1f\",\"$L20\",\"$L21\",\"$L22\",\"$L23\",\"$L24\",\"$L25\",\"$L26\",\"$L27\",\"$L28\",\"$L29\",\"$L2a\",\"$L2b\",\"$L2c\",\"$L2d\",\"$L2e\",\"$L2f\",\"$L30\",\"$L31\",\"$L32\",\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\",\"$L37\",\"$L38\",\"$L39\",\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\",\"$L3c\",\"$L3d\",\"$L3e\",\"$L3f\",\"$L40\",\"$L41\",\"$L42\",\"$L43\",\"$L44\",\"$L45\",\"$L46\",\"$L47\",\"$L48\",\"$L49\",\"$L4a\",\"$L4b\",\"$L4c\",\"$L4d\",\"$L4e\",\"$L4f\",\"$L50\",\"$L51\",\"$L52\",\"$L53\"]}]]}],null,\"$L54\"]}],\"isPartial\":false,\"staleTime\":300,\"varyParams\":null,\"buildId\":\"i9Cf0qMmt9f6Hl-9FDnLU\"}\n2:[\"$\",\"p\",\"52\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Get mentioned on Nigerian media sites, blogs, and business networks. Write a guest post for a Lagos business blog. Sponsor a local event (gets mentioned on their website). Partner with complementary businesses who link to you. Local links signal 'this business serves this community.'\\r\"}]\n3:[\"$\",\"br\",\"53\",{}]\n4:[\"$\",\"p\",\"54\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Reviews: The Local SEO Multiplier\\r\"}]\n5:[\"$\",\"br\",\"55\",{}]\n6:[\"$\",\"br\",\"56\",{}]\n7:[\"$\",\"p\",\"57\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Google prioritises businesses with recent 5-star reviews. Aim for 40+ reviews (threshold for competitive rankings). After every project, email customers: 'We'd love your feedback on Google [link].' Respond to every review (positive and negative). Reviews also influence CTR  4.5? businesses get 25% more clicks than 3.5?.\\r\"}]\n8:[\"$\",\"br\",\"58\",{}]\n9:[\"$\",\"p\",\"59\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Question & Answer Management\\r\"}]\na:[\"$\",\"br\",\"60\",{}]\nb:[\"$\",\"br\",\"61\",{}]\nc:[\"$\",\"p\",\"62\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Go to your Google Business Profile, add FAQs. Customers see these before they call or visit. Example: 'How much does web design cost?' 'Do you offer payment plans?' Answer in 23 sentences, clearly. This also helps Google understand your business better.\\r\"}]\nd:[\"$\",\"br\",\"63\",{}]\ne:[\"$\",\"p\",\"64\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Local Schema Markup\\r\"}]\nf:[\"$\",\"br\",\"65\",{}]\n10:[\"$\",\"br\",\"66\",{}]\n11:[\"$\",\"p\",\"67\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Add LocalBusiness schema to your website (already done in these templates). Include: address, phone, hours, service areas. If you serve 10 cities, add ServiceArea schema listing all of them. This helps Google understand your service radius.\\r\"}]\n12:[\"$\",\"br\",\"68\",{}]\n13:[\"$\",\"br\",\"69\",{}]\n14:[\"$\",\"br\",\"70\",{}]\n15:[\"$\",\"br\",\"71\",{}]\n16:[\"$\",\"br\",\"72\",{}]\n17:[\"$\",\"p\",\"73\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"    ## Ready for Growth?\\r\"}]\n18:[\"$\",\"br\",\"74\",{}]\n19:[\"$\",\"br\",\"75\",{}]\n1a:[\"$\",\"p\",\"76\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Let our team audit your current marketing strategy and show you exactly what's holding you back.\\r\"}]\n1b:[\"$\",\"br\",\"77\",{}]\n1c:[\"$\",\"p\",\"78\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"    [Start Your Free Audit](contact.html\\\" class=\\\"btn-primary)\\r\"}]\n1d:[\"$\",\"br\",\"79\",{}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"br\",\"80\",{}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"br\",\"81\",{}]\n20:[\"$\",\"br\",\"82\",{}]\n21:[\"$\",\"br\",\"83\",{}]\n22:[\"$\",\"p\",\"84\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"        Hephzibah Media\\r\"}]\n23:[\"$\",\"br\",\"85\",{}]\n24:[\"$\",\"p\",\"86\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Nigeria's premium Digital Marketing, Tech & Print Agency. Building brands that dominate from Ogere, Ogun State.\\r\"}]\n25:[\"$\",\"br\",\"87\",{}]\n26:[\"$\",\"p\",\"88\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"        Old Ode Road, Along Ogere Tollgate, Ogere, Nigeria\\r\"}]\n27:[\"$\",\"br\",\"89\",{}]\n28:[\"$\",\"br\",\"90\",{}]\n29:[\"$\",\"p\",\"91\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"        Services\\r\"}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"br\",\"92\",{}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"p\",\"93\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"          - [Web Design](web-design.html)\\r\"}]\n2c:[\"$\",\"br\",\"94\",{}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"p\",\"95\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"          - [Digital Marketing](digital-marketing.html)\\r\"}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"br\",\"96\",{}]\n2f:[\"$\",\"p\",\"97\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"          - [SEO](seo.html)\\r\"}]\n30:[\"$\",\"br\",\"98\",{}]\n31:[\"$\",\"p\",\"99\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"          - [Graphics Design](graphics-design.html)\\r\"}]\n32:[\"$\",\"br\",\"100\",{}]\n33:[\"$\",\"br\",\"101\",{}]\n34:[\"$\",\"br\",\"102\",{}]\n35:[\"$\",\"br\",\"103\",{}]\n36:[\"$\",\"p\",\"104\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"        Resources\\r\"}]\n37:[\"$\",\"br\",\"105\",{}]\n38:[\"$\",\"p\",\"106\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"          - [Blog](blog.html)\\r\"}]\n39:[\"$\",\"br\",\"107\",{}]\n3a:[\"$\",\"p\",\"108\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\